== Quotations ==

=== 1.0 Quotations ===

Allows to quote some text.

|=Feature|=XWiki Syntax 1.0|=Result
|Simple quote|(((
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;john said this&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
I said ok
)))|(((
&gt; john said this
I said ok
)))
|Nested quotes|(((
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;john said this&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;marie answered that&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
I said ok 
)))|(((
&gt; john said this
&gt;&gt; marie answered that
I said ok
)))

